						"description": "## WebSocket Real-time Events\n\n**Connection URL:** `ws://localhost:8090/ws?token={jwt}&workspace_id={workspace_id}`\n\n### Authentication\nPass JWT token as query parameter. Workspace ID is optional but required to receive workspace events.\n\n### Events Received\n\n| Event | Description |\n|-------|-------------|\n| `execution.started` | Workflow execution began |\n| `execution.completed` | Workflow execution finished successfully |\n| `execution.failed` | Workflow execution failed |\n| `execution.cancelled` | Workflow execution was cancelled |\n| `node.started` | A node began executing |\n| `node.completed` | A node finished executing |\n| `node.failed` | A node failed |\n\n### Event Format\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"execution.started\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2025-01-01T00:00:00Z\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"execution_id\": \"uuid\",\n    \"workflow_id\": \"uuid\",\n    \"status\": \"running\",\n    \"trigger_type\": \"manual\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Client Messages\n\n**Subscribe to execution:**\n```json\n{\"type\": \"subscribe\", \"payload\": {\"execution_id\": \"uuid\"}}\n```\n\n**Subscribe to workflow:**\n```json\n{\"type\": \"subscribe\", \"payload\": {\"workflow_id\": \"uuid\"}}\n```\n\n**Unsubscribe:**\n```json\n{\"type\": \"unsubscribe\", \"payload\": {\"execution_id\": \"uuid\"}}\n```\n\n**Ping (keep-alive):**\n```json\n{\"type\": \"ping\"}\n```\n\n### Example Usage (JavaScript)\n```javascript\nconst ws = new WebSocket(`ws://localhost:8090/ws?token=${token}&workspace_id=${workspaceId}`);\n\nws.onmessage = (event) => {\n  const data = JSON.parse(event.data);\n  console.log('Event:', data.type, data.data);\n};\n\n// Subscribe to specific execution\nws.send(JSON.stringify({\n  type: 'subscribe',\n  payload: { execution_id: 'exec-uuid' }\n}));\n```"
